    {
      "id": "PopularPost57349",
      "post_content": "In one of MaRo's articles (Here's the Kicker, part of the Making Magic column), he talks about the development of certain Invasion cards. One bit of info he revealed, this card and the others of it's cycle were originaly supposed to have Kicker. The reason it was removed was during templating, it was realised that Kicker costs aren't paid until you play the spell. In other words, too late for it to allow a Sorcery to be played as an Instant. The ability had to be changed into something that isn't Kicker for it to work.",
      "posted_by": "A3Kitsune",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost57349\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">In one of MaRo's articles (Here's the Kicker, part of the Making Magic column), he talks about the development of certain Invasion cards. One bit of info he revealed, this card and the others of it's cycle were originaly supposed to have Kicker. The reason it was removed was during templating, it was realised that Kicker costs aren't paid until you play the spell. In other words, too late for it to allow a Sorcery to be played as an Instant. The ability had to be changed into something that isn't Kicker for it to work.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '57349'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy24555\">A3Kitsune</span>\r\n                                (3/2/2010 5:31:30 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"