      "id": "PopularPost231662",
      "post_content": "The best time to use it is after you've attacked with everything but before blockers are declared. Your opponent will be tapped out and unable to block, but on his next turn all of your creatures will be untapped to stop a retaliatory strike... assuming he's still alive.",
